OL,7,FA consultant paediatrician from
OL,8,FLeicester is warning young people
OL,9,Fabout the dangers of excessive use of
OL,10,Fmobile phones and social media.
OL,12,FDr Sanjiv Nichani says it's a problem
OL,13,Fthat affects the young and old but he
OL,14,Fsays it's particularly bad for the
OL,15,Fhealth and well-being of the younger
OL,16,Fgeneration who often spend hours and
OL,17,Fhours on their phones.
OL,19,FDr Nichani started his campaign to
OL,20,Fraise awareness about the issue with
OL,21,Fa visit to a school in Leicester.
